            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12 pt32 pb32">
                <p class="lead"><font style="font-size: 36px;">Designed in Switzerland. Produced in Vietnam.</font>&amp;nbsp;<br/></p>
                <p class="lead">We are an independent Swiss clothing brand, creating highly technical and durable outerwear for powder enthusiasts. We strive to inspire and trigger the urge to ride fresh powder.&amp;nbsp;<br/><br/>We are personally testing our gear on the mountain. For You! And obviously a little bit for ourselves.&amp;nbsp;<br/></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
